{"tid":474235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"執到其他人物品應該點做?  北區新腥港人：拾遺不報給予家人","createTime":"2017-11-20T03:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T05:42:02.000Z","uid":136994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ba95fc813262a7de8e78977543d4508c0be54d","tid":474235,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171120/s00011/1511114252198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171120%2Fs00011%2F1511114252198&d=s8WpbksOhz0I0illkjV7Q7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=b5e9539f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171120%2Fs00011%2F1511114252198&h=d03cb9a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171120/s00011/1511114252198</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】從小認識道德概念及情緒處理有助兒童的心理發展，浸會大學團隊花3年時間製作相關教材並在22間幼稚園試行。教學以活動為主，透過遊戲及討論等教導幼童抽象的道德觀如公平和同理心。有學者指應從小教導學生道德觀及如何處理情緒，有助其心理發展。<br />\n<br />\n浸大持續教育學院幼兒及基礎教育部助理講師殷沛淇指出，在試行教學中，可見不同地區的文化各有差異，憶述在粉嶺及港島區的幼稚園觀課時，當天教授何謂「誠實」，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中問學生若拾到他人物品應如何做。她指粉嶺區較多跨境學童，多回答給予家人；而市區的學生則指會交給警察</span>，建議教師按不同情况及配合學生背景，修改教學內容。"},{"pid":"ebe8eb69c9885c36aa859d3db5aa3dd8fec92f47","tid":474235,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d7bd98fdfcb4a41a14c01b5ddaed258605e701","tid":474235,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}